Class DistinctSignatureEnumerator

  • java.lang.Object
    • DistinctSignatureEnumerator

  • public class DistinctSignatureEnumerator
extends java.lang.Object
    Constructor processes boundaryFile through readBoundaries() producing a list of boundaries and a list of strings. A BoundaryGarden myGarden is then created from these two lists. Then run new BasicRegionGenerator for each member of myGarden.
